OL,5, Households in England face fines of up 
OL,6, to #300 and even criminal records if   
OL,7, they flout new log burner rules.       
OL,9,FA tightening of emissions regulations  
OL,10,Fhas reduced the amount of smoke new    
OL,11,Fstoves can emit per hour from 5g to 3g.
OL,13,FIt applies to homes in "smoke control  
OL,14,Fareas" which cover most of England's   
OL,15,Ftowns and cities. Anyone found to be   
OL,16,Fbreaking the new measures could be     
OL,17,Fissued with an on-the-spot fine.       
OL,19,FThe rules are part of the government's 
OL,20,Fnew 25-year environmental plan.        
